<br>
We know em..  we love em..   <br>
<br>
For us wizards our hotbuttons are like spell gems sorta..  and with additional AA exp skills...  ones we need in a moments notice on occasion..   <br>
<br>
So..  was wondering if it was possible to have free floating hot buttons..    In my set up it would be 5 on a side (left, Right) In the upper corners,  and somewhat gapped and a little spread out, Vertically ..to avoid hitting the wrong one..<br>
<br>
I dont know if its possible to free the hotkeys from the box, and I kinda doubt it.. so..  would it work if you made a hotkey box the size of the entire screen or just the top 1/4, with fade level and normal level at zero, but with normal sized hotbutton icons, pre set at the corners..  put the page switch at the very top in the center..<br>
<br>
I just think this would be and look incredible..   I want Manaburn, Flux Staff, Clickable damage, Epic and Concuss on the upper left corner and Insta-gate, Imp Familar, Fast Evac, Jboots, and random spell in the Right upper hand corner..<br>
<br>
And opinions or thoughts on if this is possible, how to code it.. or what problems I may run into? <p>Lleauaric Fyrewynd<br>Sorcerer<br>Knight of Eternal Wrath<br>Ayonae Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3749">Gear</a>


